er W.","genre_ids":[16,28,12,35],"popularity":3.0233,"vote_count":8,"poster_path":"/n6YOsMXed9z3NHIPptmAocOfh4Q.jpg","release_date":"2024-11-08","vote_average":7.857,"backdrop_path":"/AwgmO9qXGTp9q1jyzWhgOTBDgrN.jpg","original_title":"風都探偵 仮面ライダースカルの肖像","original_language":"ja"},{"id":1144107,"adult":false,"title":"The Legend of Hei 2","video":false,"overview":"When an attack shatters the fragile peace between the spirit world and humanity, Hei teams up with Luye, the last disciple of his Shifu Wuxian, to expose a conspiracy that threatens both realms - and the bond they've sworn to protect.","genre_ids":[16,14,28],"popularity":6.4349,"vote_count":43,"poster_path":"/l1Q7YzanazjJescEkSfcRuIj1hR.jpg","release_date":"2025-07-18","vote_average":8.442,"backdrop_path":"/uJEZaEM2hY3MG50CgZ3z9jeTwmp.jpg","original_title":"罗小黑战记 2","original_language":"zh"},{"id":9320,"adult":false,"title":"The Avengers","video":false,"overview":"British Ministry agent John Steed, under direction from \"Mother\", investigates a diabolical plot by arch-villain Sir August de Wynter to rule the world with his weather control machine. Steed investigates the beautiful Doctor Mrs. Emma Peel, the only suspect, but simultaneously falls for her and joins forces with her to combat Sir August.","genre_ids":[28,12,53,878,35],"popularity":2.2525,"vote_count":762,"poster_path":"/1p5thyQ4pCy876HpdvFARqJ62N9.jpg","release_date":"1998-08-13","vote_average":4.442,"backdrop_path":"/nMjfRk5SBNuxT01f5FYO5rJLwnI.jpg","original_title":"The Avengers","original_language":"en"},{"id":9334,"adult":false,"title":"The Scorpion King","video":false,"overview":"In ancient Egypt, peasant Mathayus is hired to exact revenge on the powerful Memnon and the sorceress Cassandra, who are ready to overtake Balthazar's village. Amid betrayals, thieves, abductions and more, Mathayus strives to bring justice to his complicated world.","genre_ids":[28,12,14],"popularity":4.188,"vote_count":3316,"poster_path":"/aITIsX20tACn6jgtyDcCYpRT2